overview: It all started as just another Pussyman spectacular - only this time the action was to take place on a luxury yacht, with Pussyman and his kinky crew giving new meaning to the term "pleasure cruise." After a full day of hardcore hi-jinx on the high seas, they sailed back to port - only to sink just a few miles from shore! With their Coast Guard rescue covered by the national press, this is the first non-stop Pussyman party to end with a completely different kind of climax!
tagline: Now sit right down and you'll hear a tale, a tale of a fateful trip...
title: Pussyman 15: Bone Voyage
